onal information, with our governmental and other partners to help detect, deter, and prosecute suspected criminal activity. We also disclose personal information when required by law or to comply with a judicial proceeding, a subpoena, a court order, or other legal process or request, to defend our rights and property, to investigate suspicious activity, and otherwise in connection with legal proceedings and investigations.\r\n\r\nCon Edison has implemented policy guidelines and security features to access specific customer-account information and to help safeguard customer-specific account information from unauthorized access or improper use.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #0099d8;\"><strong>Information We Gather When You Use Our Site</strong></span>\r\n\r\nCon Edison uses software to automatically collect non-personal information about your visit for statistical purposes. This information, such as the name of the domain from which you access the Internet, the date and time you access our website, and the information you view while visiting our website, is used to measure the use of our site, to improve its content, and to diagnose and correct technical problems.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Privacy Policy','','inherit','closed','closed','','17-revision-v1','','','2015-11-17 15:35:32','2015-11-17 15:35:32','',17,'http://coned.staging.click3x.com/?p=368',0,'revision','',0),(369,1,'2015-11-17 18:16:44','2015-11-17 18:16:44','','Featured Events','','publish','closed','closed','','acf_featured-events','','','2015-11-17 18:31:26','2015-11-17 18:31:26','',0,'http://coned.staging.click3x.com/?post_type=acf&#038;p=369',0,'acf','',0),(370,1,'2015-11-17 18:24:11','2015-11-17 18:24:11','','Events Calendar','','inherit','closed','closed','','216-revision-v1','','','2015-11-17 18:24:11','2015-11-17 18:24:11','',216,'http://coned.staging.click3x.com/?p=370',0,'revision','',0),(375,1,'2015-11-17 18:31:10','2015-11-17 18:31:10','','Events Calendar','','inherit','closed','clos